PSG Results: Calculated - Wake time after sleep onset (WASO) (minutes)
calculation: waso = timebedp - slpprdp - slplatp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Sleep latency (minutes)
description: same as slplatp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total sleep time (minutes)
description: same as slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total time in bed (minutes)
description: same as timebedp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Sleep efficiency (%)
description: missing if timebedp = 0
calculation: slp_eff = 100*(slpprdp)/timebedp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Sleep maintenance efficiency (%)
description: % of time spent asleep between sleep onset and lights on
calculation: slp_maint_eff = 100*(slpprdp/(timebedp-slplatp))

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep time in stage 1 sleep (%)
description: same as tmstg1p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg1/stg2

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total sleep time in stage 1 sleep (minutes)
description: same as minstg1p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg1/stg2

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep time in stage 2 sleep (%)
description: same as tmstg2p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg1/stg2 or stg2/stag3

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total sleep time in stage 2 sleep (minutes)
description: same as minstg2p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg1/stg2 or stg2/stag3

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep time in stage 3-4 sleep (%)
description: same as tmstg34p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg3/stg4

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total sleep time in stage 3-4 sleep (minutes)
description: same as minstg34p; missing if study with problems scoring sleep/wake or stg3/stg4

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep time in REM sleep (%)
description: same as tmremp; missing if study with problems scoring REM/NREM

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Total sleep time in REM sleep (minutes)
description: same as minremp; missing if study with problems scoring REM/NREM

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - REM Latency I - including wake time (minutes)
description: same as remlaip; missing if study scored as sleep/wake (minutes)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep in supine body position (%)
description: missing if position sensor in not working
calculation: supinep = 100*(remepbp+nremepbp)/(remepbp+nremepbp+remepop+nremepop)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Percent sleep time in non-supine body position (%)
description: missing if position sensor in not working
calculation: nsupinep = 100*(remepop+nremepop)/(remepbp+nremepbp+remepop+nremepop)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Arousal index for sleep in all stages
description: missing if study scored as sleep/wake or where arousals were ignored or if total sleep time is 0
calculation: ai_all = 60*(arrembp + arremop + arnrembp + arnremop)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Arousal index for sleep in REM stage
description: missing if study scored as sleep/wake or where arousals were ignored or where time in REM is zero
calculation: ai_rem = 60*(arrembp + arremop)/minremp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Arousal index for sleep in NREM stage
description: missing if study scored as sleep/wake or where arousals were ignored
calculation: ai_nrem = 60*(arnrembp + arnremop)/(slpprdp - minremp)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI (>= 0% desaturation)
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: rdim0p = 60*(hrembp + hrop + hnrbp + hnrop + carbp + carop + canbp + canop +oarbp +oarop + oanbp + oanop + marbp + marop + manrbp + manrop)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI (>= 2% desaturation)
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: rdim2p = 60*(hrembp2 + hrop2 + hnrbp2 + hnrop2 + carbp2 + carop2 + canbp2 + canop2 + oarbp2 + oarop2 + oanbp2 + oanop2 + marbp2 + marop2 + manrbp2 + manrop2)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI (>= 3% desaturation)
description: missing if total sleep time is 1
calculation: rdim3p = 60*(hrembp3 + hrop3 + hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + carbp3 + carop3 + canbp3 + canop3 + oarbp3 + oarop3 + oanbp3 + oanop3 + marbp3 + marop3 + manrbp3 + manrop3)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI (>= 4% desaturation)
description: missing if total sleep time is 4
calculation: rdim4p = 60*(hrembp4 + hrop4 + hnrbp4 + hnrop4 + carbp4 + carop4 + canbp4 + canop4 + oarbp4 + oarop4 + oanbp4 + oanop4 + marbp4 + marop4 + manrbp4 + manrop4)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI (>= 5% desaturation)
description: missing if total sleep time is 3
calculation: rdim5p = 60*(hrembp5 + hrop5 + hnrbp5 + hnrop5 + carbp5 + carop5 + canbp5 + canop5 + oarbp5 + oarop5 + oanbp5 + oanop5 + marbp5 + marop5 + manrbp5 + manrop5)/slpprdp

calculation: rdim5pa = 60*(hremba5 +hroa5 + hnrba5 + hnroa5 +carba5+ caroa5 + canba5 + canoa5 + oarba5 + oaroa5 + oanba5 + oanoa5 + marbpa5 + maropa5 + manrbpa5 + manropa5)/slpprdp

description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 1
calculation: rdimrem3p = 60*(hrembp3 + hrop3 + carbp3 + carop3 + oarbp3 + oarop3 + marbp3 + marop3) / minremp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in REM sleep (>= 4% desaturation)

calculation: rdimrem4p = 60*(hrembp4 + hrop4 + carbp4 + carop4 + oarbp4 + oarop4 + marbp4 + marop4) / minremp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in REM sleep (>= 5% desaturation)
description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 3
calculation: rdimrem5p = 60*(hrembp5 + hrop5 + carbp5 + carop5 + oarbp5 + oarop5 + marbp5 + marop5) / minremp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in NREM sleep (>= 0% desaturation)

calculation: rdimnr0p  = 60*(hnrbp + hnrop + canbp + canop + oanbp +oanop + manrbp + manrop)/(slpprdp - minremp)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in NREM sleep (>= 2% desaturation)
description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 0
calculation: rdimnr2p  = 60*(hnrbp2 + hnrop2 + canbp2 + canop2 + oanbp2 + oanop2 + manrbp2 + manrop2)/(slpprdp - minremp)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in NREM sleep (>= 3% desaturation)
description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 1
calculation: rdimnr3p  = 60*(hnrbp3 + hnrop3 + canbp3 + canop3 + oanbp3 + oanop3 + manrbp3 + manrop3)/(slpprdp - minremp)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in NREM sleep (>= 4% desaturation)
description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 4

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - RDI in NREM sleep (>= 5% desaturation)
description: missing if studies with problems scoring REM/NREM or if studies scored as sleep/wake or NREM sleep time is 3

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Obstructive apnea (all desats) Hypopnea (3% desat) Index
description: missing if total sleep time is 1

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Obstructive apnea index (4% desats)

calculation: oai4p  = 60*(oarbp4 + oarop4 + oanbp4 + oanop4)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Obstructive/Mixed Apnea Index (4% desats) with arousals

calculation: omai4pa = 60*(oarba4 + oaroa4 + oanba4 + oanoa4 + marbpa + maropa + manrbpa + manropa)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Central apnea index (4% desats)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Minimum SaO2 during sleep (%)
calculation: minsat = min(losao2r,losao2nr)

description: missing if total sleep time is 0

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Apnea hypopnea index (3% desats) in back
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: omahi3b = 60*(oarbp + oanbp + marbp +  manrbp + hremba3 + hnrba3)/(remepbp + nremepbp)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Apnea hypopnea index (3% desats) in other
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: omahi3o = 60*(oarop + oanop + marop + manrop + hroa3 + hnroa3)/(remepop + nremepop)

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Hypopnea index (all desats)
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: hi0p = 60*(hrembp + hrop + hnrbp + hnrop)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Mixed apnea index (all desats)
description: missing if total sleep time is 0
calculation: mai0p = 60*(marbpa + maropa + manrbpa + manropa)/slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Oxygen desaturation index (ODI) 3%
calculation: odi3 = ((dsrem3 * minremp) + (dsnr3 * (slp_time - minremp))) / slpprdp

display_name: PSG Results: Calculated - Oxygen desaturation index (ODI) 4%
calculation: odi4 = ((dsrem4 * minremp) + (dsnr4 * (slp_time - minremp))) / slpprdp
